o Bank Account<a href="#pay-in-withdraw-fiat" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 4. Move USD to Bank Account" title="Direct link to 4. Move USD to Bank Account">​</a></h3><p>To manage on-platform cash balances, use the <a href="/api/v2#tag/Fiat-Transfers">Fiat Transfers</a> APIs to batch withdraw USD to any designated bank account as needed.
Learn more in the <a href="/developer/fiat-transfers">fiat transfers guide</a>.</p><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip alert alert--success admonition_WoCw"><div class="admonitionHeading_TMsN"><span class="admonitionIcon_Ibzs"><svg class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeMedium css-1y2u31q" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-testid="CheckCircleOutlinedIcon"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm4.59-12.42L10 14.17l-2.59-2.58L6 13l4 4 8-8z"></path></svg></span>Before You Begin</div><div class="admonitionContent_vXIg"><p>If you need to <a href="/api/v2#tag/Fiat-Transfers/operation/CreateFiatAccount">create a fiat account</a> Paxos may need to enable some API functionality.
<a href="https://paxos.com/stablecoin-and-payments/#contact-us-form" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Contact us</a> or reach out to your Paxos Representative for assistance.</p></div></div><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="refunds">Set Up a Refund Workflow<a href="#refunds" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Set Up a Refund Workflow" title="Direct link to Set Up a Refund Workflow">​</a></h2><p>To process stablecoin refunds on the Paxos Platform, first <a href="/payments/quickstart#refund-fund-account">fund your account with USD</a> then use  <a href="/api/v2#tag/Crypto-Withdrawals/operation/CreateCryptoWithdrawal">Create Crypto Withdrawal</a> to initiate a stablecoin refund to the Buyer.
Once a refund is complete, the transaction shows up in the <a href="/api/v2#tag/Transfers/operation/ListTransfers">List Transfers</a> monitoring and reconciliation polling request.</p><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="refund-fund-account">1. Add USD to a Refund Account<a href="#refund-fund-account" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 1. Add USD to a Refund Account" title="Direct link to 1. Add USD to a Refund Account">​</a></h3><p>Production implementations can use the <a href="/api/v2#tag/Fiat-Transfers">Fiat Transfers</a> APIs to send USD to a destination on the Paxos Platform, which is out of scope for this guide.
The <a href="/developer/fiat-transfers">fiat transfers guide</a> provides step-by-step instructions on setting up fiat movements.</p><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip alert alert--success admonition_WoCw"><div class="admonitionHeading_TMsN"><span class="admonitionIcon_Ibzs"><svg class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeMedium css-1y2u31q" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-testid="CheckCircleOutlinedIcon"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm4.59-12.42L10 14.17l-2.59-2.58L6 13l4 4 8-8z"></path></svg></span>Before You Begin</div><div class="admonitionContent_vXIg"><ul><li>If you need to <a href="/api/v2#tag/Fiat-Transfers/operation/CreateFiatAccount">create a fiat account</a> Paxos may need to enable some API functionality.
<a href="https://paxos.com/stablecoin-and-payments/#contact-us-form" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Contact us</a> or reach out to your Paxos Representative for assistance.</li></ul></div></div><p>For simplicity, this guide uses <a href="/api/v2#tag/Sandbox-Deposits/operation/CreateSandboxDeposit">Create Sandbox Deposit</a> to simulate funding the designated Seller Profile with USD.
Include the Seller&#x27;s Profile ID (<code>profile_id</code>) as a path parameter, as well as the deposit <code>asset</code> and <code>amount</code> as query parameters.</p><div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#F8F8F2;--prism-background-color:#282A36"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">curl</span><span class="token plain"> --location </span><span class="token string" style="color:rgb(255, 121, 198)">&#x27;https://api.sandbox.paxos.com/v2/sandbox/profiles/eb1dbb95-8e22-471b-9ded-40bbfe309037/deposit&#x27;</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:rgb(248, 248, 242)">\</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">--header </span><span class="token string" style="color:rgb(255, 121, 198)">&#x27;Content-Type: application/json&#x27;</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:rgb(248, 248, 242)">\</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">--header </span><span class="token string" style="color:rgb(255, 121, 198)">&#x27;Accept: application/json&#x27;</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:rgb(248, 248, 242)">\</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">--header </span><span class="token string" style="color:rgb(255, 121, 198)">&#x27;Authorization: Bearer {access_token} \</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token string" style="color:rgb(255, 121, 198)">--data &#x27;</span><span class="token punctu